Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.84,0:00:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坂本...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.81,0:00:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在...你在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.31,0:00:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坂本...坂本！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.41,0:00:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会这样...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.41,0:00:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.51,0:00:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他丢下我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.71,0:00:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留下我一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.41,0:00:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.26,0:00:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伤者就得置身事外吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.93,0:00:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.69,0:00:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被丢开了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么都不告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.57,0:00:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不回来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.28,0:00:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芯片的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.13,0:00:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是不得已 我也不是想瞒着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.81,0:00:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在做我的工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.81,0:00:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坂本你不也是...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.12,0:00:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相互竞争
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.01,0:00:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞒着我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.74,0:00:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先下手为强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.59,0:00:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先下手为强...！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.41,0:00:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是有6枚芯片了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.81,0:00:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁都信不过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.07,0:00:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.16,0:00:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.04,0:00:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些芯片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.89,0:00:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是随手捡的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.21,0:00:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但只是我想拿来做保险
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.73,0:01:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.06,0:01:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样不行 好想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.41,0:01:04.68,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,再这样会死
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.77,0:01:05.46,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,我好想见...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:06.54,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,不想死...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.57,0:01:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好想见你...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.99,0:01:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好想见你啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.76,0:01:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.09,0:01:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是...是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.67,0:01:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁...谁在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.34,0:01:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回来了吗 坂本？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.82,0:01:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.80,0:01:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 刚才那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.99,0:01:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我终于也出现幻觉...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.22,0:01:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.13,0:01:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚彦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.24,0:01:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.88,0:01:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底什么时候到这里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.90,0:02:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.47,0:02:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想...见你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.92,0:02:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不快点回来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.72,0:02:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这么说我也没办法啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.72,0:02:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好想见爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.35,0:02:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.02,0:02:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 爸爸 我受了重伤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.43,0:02:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且 芯片还没有收齐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.71,0:02:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家想见爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.72,0:02:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想见你啊 这还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.76,0:02:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 芯片...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.71,0:02:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八枚芯片...还没拿到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.83,0:02:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.37,0:02:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昭子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子他爸 你已经呆到连数都数不清了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.39,0:02:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说...数？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在又几枚芯片？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.17,0:02:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芯 芯片有...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.05,0:03:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一 二...三
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样可不够啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.96,0:03:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 还...有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四 五 六
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.78,0:03:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七 八！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.19,0:03:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回 回 回得去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.65,0:03:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等着我 柚彦 昭子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.78,0:03:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸会回去的 会回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.96,0:03:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后一起去吃大餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.80,0:03:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到味乃家去吃大吃特吃煎饼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.07,0:03:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,染成赤红的指南针
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.53,0:03:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不断的映入眼眶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I defy the beating of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.34,0:04:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,深陷死亡的亢奋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.58,0:04:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,充满矛盾的痛楚 仿佛在确认生命的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I m left tolick my wounds again
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.88,0:04:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,REAL 渐渐解开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.21,0:04:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不断见到孤独中的人影
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.95,0:04:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,扭曲的梦destroy my existence now
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在 在四散碎裂的世界之中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舍弃束搏自己的枷锁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.34,0:04:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沉溺与这种诱惑 disillusion delusion
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾几 何时失落的鲜明的岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也在忘却一切的瞬间 resolution redemption
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.33,0:04:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天也要将战斗握在手中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.50,0:04:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so take hold
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just watch a new world as it will unfold
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:05:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dont go of your vision
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just take life head on and find your reason
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起雾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.87,0:05:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且太阳也基本下山了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巨蜥们就要醒来 快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.56,0:05:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘘 好像能听到...什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是巨蜥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.36,0:05:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 这声音...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.39,0:05:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难不成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是追踪式炸弹！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.26,0:06:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龙太！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被锁定了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.14,0:06:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龙太 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.67,0:06:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不妙 进入其爆范围的话就会爆炸的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.75,0:06:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追踪式炸弹...拥有这种炸弹的是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难不成！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.61,0:06:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平先生！ 如果是你 请你住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.24,0:06:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是同伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龙太 后面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 还在起爆范围内
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龙太
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 脚...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.08,0:07:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平先生 求求你 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要做这么过分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.04,0:07:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要做这种事 为什么..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.59,0:07:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,集齐6枚芯片的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.27,0:07:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个人就将要受到考验
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.81,0:07:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道平先生是集齐了芯片 所以就背叛了我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.55,0:07:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.75,0:07:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,究竟藏在什么地方 那个老狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么背叛我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:08:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是说好了一起离开的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.47,0:08:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.86,0:08:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总免不了产生你会不会不回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会不会抛弃我了的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.94,0:08:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,满脑子都是这些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.53,0:08:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要不要不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.78,0:08:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次真的撑不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是你现在抛下我 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.49,0:08:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会崩溃的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了给平先生疗伤 也需要干净的毛巾和水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.27,0:08:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必担心 我们会拿到很多好吃的回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因为我的错吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.64,0:08:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果平先生有这么做的理由 那就是我让他感到不安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.28,0:08:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他明明那么害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.52,0:08:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我却为什么没有发觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.61,0:08:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就好像我 像我在不知不觉中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.05,0:08:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做了和老爸一样的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.03,0:09:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老爸是个工作狂 对我不理不睬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.88,0:09:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老妈自作主张离婚 又自作主张带来了继父
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.89,0:09:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大人都很自私 事事只考虑自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.59,0:09:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,装出一副很喜欢我的样子 然后自我满足
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我却把己所不欲加与平先生了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.35,0:09:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我忽视了平先生的心情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.26,0:09:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.85,0:09:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是这样逃避现实的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龙太 龙太!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.16,0:09:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振作一点 炸弹的声音又传来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动作快 得从这儿逃走才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龙太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.09,0:09:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 卑弥呼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.03,0:10:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们现在玩游戏和BTOOOM规则相同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么遥控式炸弹应该也和网络里的性能一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.18,0:10:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就不能犹豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.71,0:10:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能犹豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卑弥呼！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.46,0:10:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.87,0:10:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有被锁定的目标进入起爆氛围才会爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来保护 龙太由我来保护
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这...难道是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.48,0:10:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卑弥呼就是我在BTOOOM里面遇到的那个卑弥呼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平先生没有移动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 他一定藏在能看到我们的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.84,0:11:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卑弥呼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.26,0:11:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 遥控式炸弹只能锁定一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.75,0:11:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坂本 卑弥呼 你们别怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是游戏 我也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.32,0:11:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 是这样吧 柚彦 昭子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.33,0:11:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:11:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:12:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听得到 在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.83,0:12:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来几次都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.69,0:12:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像 有点不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是想杀我 怎么会用这么单纯的攻击手法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.61,0:12:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对 他不会这么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.66,0:12:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一手大有来头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是这样 那颗炸弹的目标是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.46,0:12:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平先生的目标是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.02,0:12:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卑弥呼 是你！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 料中了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.25,0:12:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被 被看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟 糟糕 糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这 这下惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.31,0:12:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平先生！平先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.81,0:13:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 会被杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.44,0:13:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.99,0:13:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别再做这种事了 请回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.07,0:13:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龙太
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.74,0:13:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龙太！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.94,0:13:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 我的腰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.13,0:13:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.40,0:13:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会被杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.78,0:13:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就剩下...一个了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.43,0:13:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在被杀之前 先杀了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.81,0:13:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了柚彦 为了昭子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平先生！你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.47,0:13:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平先生 我想向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.54,0:14:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和平先生一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.29,0:14:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会再让你感到不安了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次我会好好干的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.58,0:14:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你 再给我一次机会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.67,0:14:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 平先生 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我向你道歉吧 平先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.51,0:14:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.66,0:14:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阪 阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.37,0:14:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我 我 我...我...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.04,0:14:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓因果报应吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.17,0:14:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是对我所做过的事的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.74,0:14:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不住了 阪本 卑弥呼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.43,0:14:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想回家而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.93,0:15:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是 想见家人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.19,0:15:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚彦 昭子 对不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.71,0:15:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸好痛苦 已经受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.07,0:15:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平 平...先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.17,0:15:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是要一起回去的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.48,0:15:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站起来啊 说句话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.20,0:15:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像往常那样说个无聊的笑话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杯面泡两分钟就吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:16:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都 还没向 平先生道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.95,0:16:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.51,0:16:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平先生 是不是一开始就打算背叛我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.86,0:16:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像伊达先生那样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 平先生不是那样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他只是个普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.71,0:16:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正因为是普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.79,0:16:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才会吃惊 才会怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.20,0:16:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都爱惜自己的生命 都想早点回家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.42,0:16:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 受了重伤被一个人丢下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.89,0:16:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被绝望逼得走投无路的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.95,0:16:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平先生的心就崩溃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.60,0:16:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像是我 就像是我杀的一样 是我...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龙太 你也想回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.31,0:17:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 真想立刻就逃离这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃离这种屎一样的地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.35,0:17:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以回去的 龙太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.53,0:17:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以...回去？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.58,0:17:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 这是刚才回收的芯片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一枚是平先生的 另两枚是平先生悄悄收集的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.54,0:17:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这三枚和我们所收集的加一起就有六枚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我还有一枚 龙太也有一枚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样有权离开岛的八枚芯片就齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要我们之中有一个人死去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.86,0:17:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另一个人就能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.77,0:17:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 杀了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.02,0:18:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经没有归宿了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.82,0:18:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有你改变了无处可去的我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在现实中明明并无交集
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却有种心灵相通的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.34,0:18:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即便是在虚拟的世界中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.68,0:18:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也拯救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.48,0:18:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而在来到这个岛上之后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.94,0:18:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我无数次命悬一线 即将崩溃的时候也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.38,0:18:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我清楚的明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.55,0:18:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龙太是我活下去的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龙太 如果龙太能得救
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.32,0:18:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我无论变成什么样 无论会怎么样都...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开 开什么玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我有那么想回去 甚至不惜牺牲你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.83,0:18:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我是那种人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.07,0:19:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么会抛弃你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.65,0:19:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不可能抛弃你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.55,0:19:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论是现实中 还是在虚拟世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.32,0:19:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卑弥呼 你就是那个卑弥呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.19,0:19:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我总算发觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.43,0:19:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总算见到你了 卑弥呼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.48,0:19:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直 一直很想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卑弥呼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 她现在也还是很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.41,0:20:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明应该很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却为了我 拚命地忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.24,0:20:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.45,0:20:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.59,0:20:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我应该告诉过你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.51,0:20:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有行动才会取胜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿出男子气概来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.05,0:20:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是你又要束博自己 然后自我满足？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.74,0:20:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.04,0:21:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 你一辈子也别想超过我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.35,0:21:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴！ 我已经不再...憧景你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.19,0:21:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.92,0:21:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是珍惜他人的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.27,0:21:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是我能明白这点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.98,0:21:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平先生就不会死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.10,0:21:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也能好好地面对家人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.16,0:21:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以为只有自己是特别的 自以为是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.41,0:21:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞧不起别人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.15,0:21:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.20,0:21:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就压根不会被带到这个岛上来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.94,0:21:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,织田 我和你不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.07,0:21:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会变成像你那样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.19,0:21:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别赖在我的心里了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.74,0:22:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龙太？怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.34,0:22:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 突然推倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.86,0:22:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 在这种地方顺势...总觉得 不太对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.89,0:22:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卑弥呼 一起离开这个岛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.89,0:22:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.00,0:22:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我们回去...等我们回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.97,0:22:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就正式向你提出交往
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.94,0:22:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.75,0:22:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.99,0:22:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和卑弥呼一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.97,0:22:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,离开这个地域
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.60,0:22:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,24小时 说什么都要在24小时之内修复
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.90,0:23:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了岛上后  尽快的展开修复！明白了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.17,0:23:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白 那我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.38,0:23:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这件事绝对不能让客户知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.51,0:23:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.39,0:23:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈的 岛上的设备居然偏偏在这重要的时候故障
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.30,0:23:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靠 到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.99,0:23:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龙太 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.67,0:23:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能做到的就只有这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.74,0:22:34.36,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,最果ての{\fs60}STORY{\r}抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.51,0:22:38.24,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,あてもなく{\fs60}彷徨い{\r}続けた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.67,0:22:40.92,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,滲{\r}んだ new world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.09,0:22:44.03,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,The game has only just begun
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.16,0:22:46.44,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,終焉{\r}のEYES
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.33,0:22:49.67,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where tomorrow brings a new game
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.67,0:22:52.54,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to learn that pain is gain ready {\fs60}FIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.61,0:23:04.99,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,過去の失望{\fs60}塗{\r}りつぶすために
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.05,0:23:07.64,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,犠牲{\r}にしてきた未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.76,0:23:09.64,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,ライフ\N僕の{\fs60}命{\r}が尽きるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.85,0:23:12.72,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,その定めぶち{\fs60}壊{\r}していくのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.03,0:23:16.69,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,嗚呼 Break out and start a revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.69,0:23:21.93,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,一つの答えを{\fs60}探{\r}して
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.24,0:23:25.01,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,限界の{\fs60}RACE{\r}に挑んで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.01,0:23:27.54,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,一度切りのチャンスと{\fs60}知{\r}って
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.42,0:23:31.92,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,背負った{\fs60}運命{\r}越えていくんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.29,0:23:35.03,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,最果ての{\fs60}STORY{\r}抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.18,0:23:39.19,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,あてもなく{\fs60}彷徨い{\r}続けた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.43,0:23:42.02,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,滲{\r}んだ new world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.33,0:23:44.43,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,The game has only just begun
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.92,0:23:49.97,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,今{\fs60}終焉{\r}のEYES
